(1435, 1, '2011-12-23 15:21:16', '2011-12-23 14:21:16', 'Coupling Wave Solutions (CWS) is an EDA (Electronic Design Automation) software publisher.\r\n\r\nThese software are designed for the industry of semi-conductors and answer to signal integrity problems (signal continuity, electro-migration, signal delay…) happening in complex systems like System on Chip (SoC) or System in Package (SiP).\r\n\r\nCWS offers a global software response dedicated to the successful integration of digital, analogical and RF (radio-frequency) blocks in complex SoC and SiP.', 'CWS', 'Coupling Wave Solutions (CWS) is an EDA (Electronic Design Automation) software publisher.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cws', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:08:08', '2016-06-14 14:08:08', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1435', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1437, 1, '2011-12-23 15:22:16', '2011-12-23 14:22:16', '<!--:en-->Ercom develops products with highly technological content, designed for telecom networks testing, measurement and securing. These products include next generation 4G networks. Ercom has a cutting edge technology and owns a significant portfolio of patents developed by a team of 80 specialized engineers.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Ercom', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ercom', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:07:14', '2016-06-14 14:07:14', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1437', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1441, 1, '2011-12-23 15:23:46', '2011-12-23 15:23:46', '<!--:en-->European travel search engine.\r\n\r\nSold to SNCF Voyages in 2010.\r\n\r\nSold to Odigeo in 2013.<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'Liligo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'liligo', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:06:35', '2016-06-14 14:06:35', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1441', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1443, 1, '2011-12-23 15:24:38', '2011-12-23 15:24:38', '<!--:en-->MakeMeReach is an agency specialized in social networks. It is also the first company in the world to obtain the three Facebook accreditations. MakeMeReach helps advertisers with their communication on social networks and optimizes quickly and simply the monetization of main publishers’ traffic. MakeMeReach is among the leading French agencies on the social networks segment.\r\n\r\nSold to Perion Network Ltd. (NASDAQ: PERI) in 2015<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'MakeMeReach', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'makemereach', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:05:16', '2016-06-14 14:05:16', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1443', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1445, 1, '2011-12-23 15:25:32', '2011-12-23 14:25:32', 'Falguière Conseil is the publisher of the website MeilleursAgents.com.\r\n\r\nLaunched at the end of 2008, MeilleursAgents.com is the leading French player in the field of property valuation thanks to a complete, free and personalized proprietary tool of valuation. MeilleursAgents.com is a “broker” of estate agencies: the owner a real estate property signs a brokerage contract with MeilleursAgents.com, which is then executed by two agencies of its network.\r\n\r\nMeilleursAgents.com controls each step of the contract execution. The company is active in Ile de France and PACA regions, and progressively extends its presence to the other regions of France.', 'MeilleursAgents', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'meilleursagents', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:03:52', '2016-06-14 14:03:52', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1445', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1447, 1, '2011-12-23 15:26:19', '2011-12-23 15:26:19', '<!--:en-->Video game online distribution platform.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Metaboli', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'metaboli', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:01:23', '2016-06-14 14:01:23', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1447', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1451, 1, '2011-12-23 15:28:11', '2011-12-23 15:28:11', '<!--:en-->MobPartner is a mobile international affiliation platform. The platform aggregates hundreds of thousands websites, services, mobile applications publishers and proposes it to its advertisers-partners on a performance-based model. The choice of performance-focused marketing guarantees return on investment. MobPartner is at the crossroad of two potentially high-growth markets: mobile and performance-based advertising.\r\n\r\nSold to Cheetah Mobile Inc. (NYSE: CMCM) in 2015<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'MobPartner', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mobpartner', '', '', '2016-06-14 14:00:25', '2016-06-14 14:00:25', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1451', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1453, 1, '2011-12-23 15:28:55', '2011-12-23 15:28:55', '<!--:en-->Monshowroom is an online womenswear and accessories retailer. Founded in 2006 by two young entrepreneurs, Séverine Grégoire and Chloé Ramade, Monshowroom.com sells in France in-season collections of numerous trendy brands like: American Vintage, Antik Batik, Ba&amp;Sh, French Connection, Iro, Paul&amp;Joe Sister… Located in Marseille, the company aims to become a leading online shopping website, targeting young, urban and active women in France and Europe.\r\n\r\nSold to Casino in 2012.<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'MonShowroom', 'Monshowroom is an online womenswear and accessories retailer.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'monshowroom', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:59:28', '2016-06-14 13:59:28', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1453', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1455, 1, '2011-12-23 15:29:32', '2011-12-23 15:29:32', '<!--:en-->E-commerce of furniture/interior decoration, based on a made-to-order manufacturing concept. MyFab makes design more accessible by offering the best prices for innovative and qualitative products for home and leisure activities. By suppressing intermediation, unnecessary margins and thanks to the direct access to 300 factories all around the world, internet users benefit from made-to-order quality products at the best price, directly delivered at home.\r\n\r\nSold to Fab.com in 2013.', 'MyFab', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'myfab', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:58:03', '2016-06-14 13:58:03', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1455', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1461, 1, '2011-12-23 15:33:11', '2011-12-23 15:33:11', '<!--:en-->Plantes &amp; Jardins is a media and e-commerce website specialized in gardening. Thanks to a very rich content composed of product descriptions of thousands of plants and accessories, Plantes &amp; Jardins has been for 10 years the reference website for plant, outdoor furniture and accessories online shopping in France. With a traffic of more than one million monthly visits, Plantes &amp; Jardins is profitable since 2009 and is now self-financing its growth.\r\n\r\nSold in 2012 to Gamm Vert.<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'Plantes et Jardins', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'plantes-et-jardins', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:57:02', '2016-06-14 13:57:02', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1461', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1463, 1, '2011-12-23 15:34:25', '2011-12-23 15:34:25', '<!--:en-->Prowebce is the French reference player on the market of communication, management and social and cultural activities of Works Councils. Prowebce helps more than 3500 Works Council, representing more than 4 million users.\r\n\r\nOriginally active on the market of management and communication software, Prowebce has developed since 2009 a platform selling products and services to the users of Works Councils with the acquisition of Meyclub.\r\n\r\nProwebce has today around €50M of revenues, is profitable since 2005 and is publicly listed on Alternext since 2010.<!--:-->', 'Prowebce', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prowebce', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:56:01', '2016-06-14 13:56:01', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1463', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1465, 1, '2011-12-23 15:35:02', '2011-12-23 15:35:02', '<!--:en-->Qosmos provides a Network Intelligence technology which offers an unprecedented insight on the network traffic. Its software development environment and its intelligent IP probes can recognize thousands of protocols and network activity. Qosmos analyses a network like a complete database, and identifies, researches and extracts traffic data with an unequaled accuracy and level of detail.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Qosmos', 'Qosmos provides a Network Intelligence technology which offers an unprecedented insight on the network traffic.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'qosmos', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:54:49', '2016-06-14 13:54:49', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1465', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1467, 1, '2011-12-23 15:35:54', '2011-12-23 15:35:54', '<!--:en-->Quelle Energie is the French reference website in terms of home energy consumption optimization. Based on a very complete energy consumption simulator, Quelle Energie enables individuals to estimate costs and gains of heating, insulation, or photovoltaic energy generation. Individuals can also contact qualified professionals to get a quote for this work. The business model is based on the sale of qualified leads to professionals of the sector. Quelle Energie has registered a strong growth since its creation in 2008 and prepares simulator solution for other segments.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'QuelleEnergie', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'quelleenergie', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:53:54', '2016-06-14 13:53:54', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1467', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1469, 1, '2011-12-23 15:36:35', '2011-12-23 15:36:35', '<!--:en-->Smallable.com is an online design and concept-store for 0-12 year-old kids. The website offers a unique selection of over 200 “trendy” designer brands found all around the world and of over 5000 references in fashion, furniture, interior decoration and toys. A design and creative offer of exclusive brands can be found on the website, as well as numerous exclusivities like the kid product range by designer Isabel Marant or furniture by the New York brand Offi.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Smallable', 'Smallable.com is an online design and concept-store for 0-12 year-old kids.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'smallable', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:52:20', '2016-06-14 13:52:20', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1469', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1471, 1, '2011-12-23 15:37:14', '2011-12-23 15:37:14', 'Splendia is the world leader of Luxury Hotel online booking. With more than 5000 referenced hotels in 130 countries, Splendia guarantees the best prices without any “hidden” additional charge. The company offers its clients exclusive advantages and an exceptional client service available 24/7.\r\n\r\nLaunched in 2004, Splendia has a team of 100 professionals mainly located in Barcelona.', 'Splendia', 'Splendia is the world leader of Luxury Hotel online booking.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'splendia', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:51:07', '2016-06-14 13:51:07', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1471', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1482, 1, '2011-12-23 16:01:04', '2011-12-23 16:01:04', '<!--:en-->CII is the controlling shareholder of the company Acute Games, which is an online game publisher specialized in the “Trading Card Games” segment (games based on virtual cards endowed with specific powers).\r\n\r\nAcute Games publishes the online game Urban Rivals, the European leader on the TCG segment with more than 20 million members among which one million players are active each month. The game is available in a hundred countries and in a dozen of languages.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Urban Rivals', 'CII is the controlling shareholder of the company Acute Games, which is an online game publisher specialized in the “Trading Card Games” segment (games based on virtual cards endowed with specific powers).', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'urban-rivals', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:49:53', '2016-06-14 13:49:53', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1482', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(1484, 1, '2011-12-23 16:02:22', '2011-12-23 16:02:22', '<!--:en-->Wanimo is the reference website in France for premium pet food products and accessories online shopping. Founded in 1999, Wanimo has registered a steady traffic and sales growth and established itself as the French leader on this segment. The company is profitable since 2011 and has a steady annual growth of 50%.\r\n\r\nSold in 2012.<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'Wanimo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wanimo', '', '', '2016-06-14 13:48:29', '2016-06-14 13:48:29', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=1484', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
