(5973, 1, '2011-01-11 17:14:03', '2011-01-11 16:14:03', '[:en]Drivy is a peer-to-peer carsharing service, that lets private car owners make money from their underused cars, and drivers find cheap and convenient rental cars in their neighborhood. The service includes a comprehensive car insurance coverage.\nDrivy was founded in 2010 in Paris, France.\nDrivy is one of the success stories of the booming collaborative consumption sector, that allows individuals to share and exchange assets, creating an economic system where access takes over ownership.[:fr]Drivy (ex Voiturelib) est un service de location de voiture entre particuliers permettant aux propriétaires d’une voiture servant peu de la rentabiliser et aux personnes ayant besoin d''une voiture d''en louer une près de chez eux, à un prix défiant toute concurrence, de manière conviviale. Le service fournit une assurance spécifique couvrant la voiture pendant la location.\nDrivy est né fin 2010, et est rapidement devenu leader de ce marché en France.\nLe service est l''une des success stories de l’économie collaborative émergente, qui permet aux individus de mettre en commun leurs biens et ainsi de faire un meilleur usage des ressources disponibles.[:]', 'Drivy', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'drivy-2__trashed', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:09:07', '2016-06-14 12:09:07', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=5973', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(5975, 1, '2013-01-11 17:16:41', '2013-01-11 16:16:41', '<!--:en-->Happyview.fr is the 1st French online optician approved. By distributing via the Web, this new generation optician provides an alternative to overpriced glasses, by proposing a large choice of eyeglasses of quality at prices 3 to 4 times lower than those applied by traditional opticians. Happyview.fr offers more than 500 models of glasses and sunglasses including major brands such as Ray-Ban, Dolce &amp; Gabbana, Versace, Ralph Lauren, Persol, Puma, Diesel, Armani etc.\r\n\r\nSold to M6 Group in 2013.<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'Happyview', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'happyview', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:56:05', '2016-06-14 12:56:05', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=5975', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(7472, 1, '2013-04-29 09:58:27', '2013-04-29 07:58:27', '<!--:en-->KelDoc has developed an internet service that allows users to easily find local doctors and dentists and make an appointment online. Patients have access to all relevant information concerning their doctor such as their tariffs, payment methods, check availability, and confirm an appointment online in a few clicks. The doctors who have subscribed to the service thus provide their patients with an innovative and convenient booking solution and also save valuable time otherwise spent every day taking appointments over the phone.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'KelDoc', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'keldoc', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:55:08', '2016-06-14 12:55:08', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=7472', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(7864, 1, '2013-06-05 17:58:08', '2013-06-05 15:58:08', '<!--:en-->Birchbox is the leading discovery commerce platform redefining the retail process by offering consumers a unique and personalized way to discover, sample, shop and learn about the best beauty and lifestyle products, and brands available.\r\n\r\nIn 2012, Birchbox acquired Paris-based JolieBox gaining business units in France, Spain and the UK in addition to the USA, taking the company global to become the international market leader in discovery commerce.<!--:-->', 'Birchbox', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'birchbox', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:54:20', '2016-06-14 12:54:20', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=7864', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(7930, 1, '2013-08-20 17:51:32', '2013-08-20 15:51:32', '<!--:en-->Leading online store offering made-to-order pieces of jewelry.\r\n\r\nGemmyo est la première marque de <a href="http://www.gemmyo.com/" target="_blank">joaillerie sur mesure</a> sur Internet. Sur Gemmyo.com, chacun peut créer le bijou de ses rêves ou sa <a href="http://www.gemmyo.com/bijoux/bagues/l/bagues-de-fiancailles.html" target="_blank">bague de fiancailles</a> en fonction de ses goûts et de son budget. Réalisées sur mesure en seulement 2 à 3 semaines, les créations Gemmyo sont façonnées dans les ateliers français de la marque pour une qualité digne des plus grandes Maisons de joaillerie.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Gemmyo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gemmyo', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:46:31', '2016-06-14 12:46:31', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=7930', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(7935, 1, '2013-09-09 17:40:42', '2013-09-09 15:40:42', '<!--:en-->OpenClassrooms / Simple IT was created in 2007 by Mathieu Nebra and Pierre Dubuc, two young entrepreneurs who are passionate about education and new technologies. The initiative aims to make educational courses accessible to all, whether beginners or not, thanks to a collaborative platform called “Site du Zéro” and the collection “Livre du Zéro.” Whether online or in print, the courses are published under the Creative Commons Open License and proving highly successful, attracting more and more students.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'OpenClassrooms', 'OpenClassrooms / Simple IT was created in 2007 by Mathieu Nebra and Pierre Dubuc, two young entrepreneurs who are passionate about education and new technologies.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'openclassrooms', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:45:38', '2016-06-14 12:45:38', '', 17, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/p=7935', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
