(26504, 1, '2016-06-14 12:55:08', '2016-06-14 12:55:08', '<!--:en-->KelDoc has developed an internet service that allows users to easily find local doctors and dentists and make an appointment online. Patients have access to all relevant information concerning their doctor such as their tariffs, payment methods, check availability, and confirm an appointment online in a few clicks. The doctors who have subscribed to the service thus provide their patients with an innovative and convenient booking solution and also save valuable time otherwise spent every day taking appointments over the phone.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'KelDoc', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7472-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:55:08', '2016-06-14 12:55:08', '', 7472, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/7472-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(26505, 1, '2016-06-14 12:56:05', '2016-06-14 12:56:05', '<!--:en-->Happyview.fr is the 1st French online optician approved. By distributing via the Web, this new generation optician provides an alternative to overpriced glasses, by proposing a large choice of eyeglasses of quality at prices 3 to 4 times lower than those applied by traditional opticians. Happyview.fr offers more than 500 models of glasses and sunglasses including major brands such as Ray-Ban, Dolce &amp; Gabbana, Versace, Ralph Lauren, Persol, Puma, Diesel, Armani etc.\r\n\r\nSold to M6 Group in 2013.<!--:--><!--:fr--><!--:-->', 'Happyview', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5975-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:56:05', '2016-06-14 12:56:05', '', 5975, 'http://stereosuper.fr/valid/alven/wp/5975-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
